Title: An Exploration of Indirect Conflicts
UseOF-SZZ: To determine whether a code change was a success or failure (introduce a software failure), the SZZ approach is used
Summary:
it focuses on the power of technical dependencies in software projects. The question I investigated were : 
    'Is it possible to identify pairs of developers whose technical dependencies in code changes statistically relate to bugs?'
Outcome: 27 statistically significant failure inducing developer pairs.
